---
title: HopperRoller State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OFF

    OFF --> ROLLING : SuperStructure sets ROLLING
    ROLLING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> PREVENT_JAM : SuperStructure sets PREVENT_JAM
    PREVENT_JAM --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    OFF --> UNJAMMING : SuperStructure sets UNJAMMING
    UNJAMMING --> OFF : SuperStructure sets OFF

    ROLLING --> PREVENT_JAM : SuperStructure sets PREVENT_JAM
    PREVENT_JAM --> ROLLING : SuperStructure sets ROLLING
    ROLLING --> UNJAMMING : SuperStructure sets UNJAMMING
    UNJAMMING --> ROLLING : SuperStructure sets ROLLING
    PREVENT_JAM --> UNJAMMING : SuperStructure sets UNJAMMING
    UNJAMMING --> PREVENT_JAM : SuperStructure sets PREVENT_JAM

    note right of OFF
        Duty cycle = 0.0
        Motor stopped
    end note

    note right of ROLLING
        Duty cycle = 0.75
        Normal feeding operation
    end note

    note right of PREVENT_JAM
        Duty cycle = -0.1
        Gentle reverse to prevent jams
    end note

    note right of UNJAMMING
        Duty cycle = -0.8
        Strong reverse to clear jams
    end note
